{"tid":11043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[LIHKG改名]諗左個中文名求巴絲打意見","createTime":"2016-11-29T07:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T07:10:11.000Z","uid":26738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b79935e072ebf625ae63fc582024897408351ec0","tid":11043,"uid":26738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:01:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的 一直以來都有好多巴絲都希望有一個中文既名唔洗咁拗口<br />\n笨撚剛剛得知datHKG決定轉會過黎加入我地大家庭 就忽發奇想諗到個中文名<br />\n&quot;香港連合討論區&quot; 連合仔都唔係好柒姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身係諗住聯合 但諗諗下個連字可以食到連尼住巴打個連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&quot;連合&quot;寓意一眾巴絲不分你我 an狗定 i狗<br />\n只要理念一致就可以共鍵大家都理想既討論區 (當然亦都可以解做聯合對抗慌丈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n係長少少 都希望大家可以比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d91c3537beff4535e7f6bdd60844f9deea8ecaf","tid":11043,"uid":26738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:05:54.000Z","msg":"原來係arcHKG 對唔住咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8155abec40a60da17152f780209bd43d76aaca","tid":11043,"uid":26738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"好唔好都比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36beec86694f4ee50ad42c7b42c6f4c3b47b90f","tid":11043,"uid":26738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:10:11.000Z","msg":"唔通連個天 都唔中意我？"}]}